1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 7=

3
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:04,672
Mr. Liao, I have a question.

4
00:01:05,126 --> 00:01:09,040
Why did you name yourself Bo Xi?

5
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,719
Just a random name.

6
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:17,879
("My husband is a brave hero
of the country.")

7
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:22,040
Ji Xuan, "Bo Xi" means husband.

8
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,799
Since we're done eating, time to leave.

9
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,120
I'll leave later.

10
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,920
Come on, I'll take you home.

11
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,400
Are you going to make me pay again?

12
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,079
No.

13
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:41,920
I'll drop you off on my way.

14
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:43,239
I'm not leaving.

15
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,120
Come on.

16
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:47,239
- I want to leave with Xuan.
- Don't go.

17
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:48,480
Wu Shu.

18
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,439
Xuan.

19
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:50,200
Wu Shu.

20
00:01:58,359 --> 00:01:59,439
Where's Wu Shu?

21
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,920
Liao Bei took her home.

22
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,000
Then why aren't you leaving?

23
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:06,319
If I leave, who will take care of you?

24
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:13,240
This will help sober you up.

25
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:18,799
I've always seen you wearing this ring.

26
00:02:19,616 --> 00:02:21,159
Does it have a special meaning?

27
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:25,479
My brother left it to me
before he passed away.

28
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:29,120
I'm sorry.

29
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,080
Ji Xuan.

30
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:46,599
How have you been all these years?

31
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,800
How have I been?

32
00:02:56,960 --> 00:03:01,400
Tell me.
Do all men like having mistresses?

33
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:02,560
Not really.

34
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,280
What about you?

35
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,479
I like excitement.

36
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:19,759
You like being a kept man?

37
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:28,319
Could you afford
to keep me as your kept man?

38
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:31,159
Is it expensive?

39
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,360
Give it a try.

40
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:02,639
I'm cold.

41
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,040
Ji Xuan.

42
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:31,000
If I had known
Xiao Jin would treat you badly,

43
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:36,040
I would never have let you go.

44
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,360
Mr. Song, we...

45
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:14,399
Miss Ji, we slept together again.

46
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,519
What? Trying to deny it again?

47
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:24,959
Mr. Song.

48
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,800
I think I drank too much last night.
I don't remember anything.

49
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:35,279
Maybe I can help you remember.

50
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:37,879
No, that won't be necessary.

51
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:45,240
Ji Xuan, since you have
broken up with Xiao Jin,

52
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,439
how about dating me?

53
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,560
Mr. Song, you know my situation well.

54
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:54,000
My ex cheated on me.

55
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:56,600
I don't have the heart
to play games with anyone.

56
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,720
Yet you keep sleeping with me

57
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:02,079
in my place and yours.

58
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:09,959
Ji Xuan.

59
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,800
You get too wild after drinking.

60
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,839
I was scared last night.

61
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,879
I'll quit drinking.

62
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:21,240
Shouldn't you compensate me a little?

63
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:22,759
What do you want?

64
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,079
Kiss me.

65
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,279
Ji Xuan.

66
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:34,959
I've been devoted to you,
yet you brush me off?

67
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,759
If you don't know how to kiss,
I'll do it.

68
00:06:43,552 --> 00:06:44,224
(Wu Shu)

69
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,040
Hello?

70
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,279
Xuan, I messed up again.

71
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,120
What happened?

72
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,360
Can you come to the hospital?

73
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,759
I broke his bones.

74
00:06:56,759 --> 00:06:59,199
The nurse said it'll be half an hour
before he wakes up.

75
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:00,160
I'm scared.

76
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,680
Okay, I'll be there soon.

77
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,160
Mr. Liao is injured.

78
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,600
Do you want to go too?

79
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,360
Here, have a sip.

80
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,120
Take a sip.

81
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,199
Mr. Liao.

82
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,399
Are you sure you got beaten up,
not in a car accident?

83
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:35,240
Didn't you say you just hit him lightly?

84
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:39,680
It looks bad,
but it's actually not that serious.

85
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:42,839
His head is wrapped like that
because his jaw was dislocated.

86
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:46,000
It's to keep him still
while he was unconscious.

87
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:50,480
His shoulder and ribs hurt.

88
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,519
Don't just look at his upper body.

89
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,639
Under the blanket, he's actually fine.

90
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,079
This isn't serious?

91
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,159
Mr. Liao.

92
00:08:01,696 --> 00:08:04,000
This is indeed Wu Shu's fault.

93
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:06,120
But she has realized her mistake.

94
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:09,680
Could you please be magnanimous
and let this go?

95
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,800
Mr. Liao, I'm so sorry.

96
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:15,279
The other day, I vandalized your car.

97
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:17,000
Last night, I beat you up.

98
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,279
Please forgive me.

99
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:21,480
I'll do my best to make it up to you.

100
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,920
She's already apologized.

101
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,120
Just forgive her.

102
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,360
How about you blink?

103
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:34,840
Once for no forgiveness,
twice for forgiveness.

104
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,624
Three times.

105
00:08:38,939 --> 00:08:42,360
It means he forgave you
for splashing paint on his car

106
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,799
and beating him.

107
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:52,000
Mr. Liao is the best employer
in Qingcheng.

108
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,080
Mr. Liao, you're such a kind person.

109
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:56,639
You both may leave.

110
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,920
I'll look after him.

111
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,240
Thank you, Mr. Song.

112
00:08:59,399 --> 00:09:01,679
Mr. Liao, you get some rest.

113
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,759
I'll take care of you like my own kin.

114
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:04,879
Come on.

115
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,754
(Outpatient)

116
00:09:19,519 --> 00:09:21,960
I didn't expect him to be so fragile.

117
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:25,960
I just touched him slightly,
and he ended up with a fracture.

118
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:28,879
You started practicing Wushu at seven.

119
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,840
It's all my dad's fault
for naming me Wu Shu.

120
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,600
He made me learn Wushu.

121
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:39,559
But I think

122
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:42,200
Song Zhaoli is actually quite decent.

123
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:45,039
He actually offered
to take care of Liao Bei.

124
00:09:47,168 --> 00:09:47,720
Wait.

125
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,679
How did you two come together?

126
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:56,200
Did you two sleep
together again last night?

127
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:58,799
We didn't.

128
00:09:59,879 --> 00:10:02,440
She was drunk yesterday
and just lay next to me.

129
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,360
So what's Song Zhaoli's attitude?

130
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:12,279
Ji Xuan broke up with Xiao Jin.

131
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,759
I'm determined
to become her new boyfriend.

132
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,960
Xuan, how do you feel about it?

133
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:23,000
Just like how you felt
after hitting Liao Bei. I feel terrible.

134
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,159
He's my client now.

135
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:27,879
And he also has a fiancée.

136
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:30,320
I don't want to get involved with him.

137
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,120
Since I'm her client,

138
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:35,120
I have countless ways
to get involved with her.

139
00:10:42,848 --> 00:10:44,928
(Outpatient)

140
00:10:46,144 --> 00:10:46,679
Mr. Zhang.

141
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,159
Xie.

142
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,320
Mr. Song will be here soon
to sign this document.

143
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,519
And I need to go out.

144
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,879
You give it to him to sign it.

145
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,559
Okay.

146
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,080
Thank you.

147
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:03,399
(Ji Xuan.)

148
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:05,559
(Since you've broken up with Xiao Jin,)

149
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,799
(how about dating me?)

150
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:12,799
(Stepping into your world
requires a bridge I can never build.)

151
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:17,799
(Song Zhaoli, what stands
between us is more than just a status.)

152
00:11:19,759 --> 00:11:20,440
Mr. Song.

153
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:22,320
Miss Ji, where are you going?

154
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:24,919
I have an urgent thing to do outside.

155
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,320
Avoiding me?

156
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,240
No, I really have something to do.

157
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:34,159
You do your work then.

158
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,159
I'm going to see Mr. Li.

159
00:11:58,202 --> 00:11:59,994
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

160
00:12:00,154 --> 00:12:02,034
♪Flickering neon lights♪

161
00:12:02,234 --> 00:12:05,562
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

162
00:12:06,074 --> 00:12:08,346
♪Every star is♪

163
00:12:08,634 --> 00:12:12,506
♪My heartbeat for you♪

164
00:12:13,818 --> 00:12:15,642
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

165
00:12:15,802 --> 00:12:17,354
♪And land in your arms♪

166
00:12:17,754 --> 00:12:21,210
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

167
00:12:21,466 --> 00:12:24,026
♪In the blue sky♪

168
00:12:24,090 --> 00:12:28,218
♪Your smile still lingers♪

169
00:12:29,146 --> 00:12:32,794
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

170
00:12:33,050 --> 00:12:36,714
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

171
00:12:36,922 --> 00:12:39,834
♪Can't find a cure♪

172
00:12:39,834 --> 00:12:44,346
♪To love you after we've parted♪

173
00:12:44,538 --> 00:12:48,570
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

174
00:12:48,570 --> 00:12:52,434
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

175
00:12:52,434 --> 00:12:54,234
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

176
00:12:54,330 --> 00:12:59,482
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

177
00:13:00,122 --> 00:13:03,834
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

178
00:13:04,026 --> 00:13:06,778
♪Can't find a cure♪

179
00:13:06,906 --> 00:13:11,546
♪To love you after we've parted♪

180
00:13:11,714 --> 00:13:15,482
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

181
00:13:15,706 --> 00:13:19,290
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

182
00:13:19,514 --> 00:13:21,554
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

183
00:13:21,554 --> 00:13:26,554
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
